<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Midnight Resistance</H1>
<TT>

<H2>CHEATS</H2>

<P>
On the title screen, type any of the following:
</P>

<P>
"ITSEASYWHENYOUKNOWHOW" --- Infinite continues<BR>
"BLUEDAY" -------------- Turns everything blue<BR>
"IAMAFREINDOFIANS" ------------------- Message<BR>
"VERSION" ----------------------- Version date<BR>
"CREDITS" ----------------------- Game credits<BR>
"HELLOS" ---------- Greeting to various people<BR>
"SIAMESE" - unlimited lives and following keys
</P>

<P>
'F1' - Normal rifle<BR>
'F2' ---- Full auto<BR>
'F3' ---- Three way<BR>
'F4' ----- Shot gun
</P>

</TT>
